Happy #Timeless day! In the final episode of Timeless, we fast forwarded to December 21, 2023. The future is now! That show meant so much to me and we had such an amazing time. People constantly ask me what was my favorite project I’ve ever been a part of as an actor… And TIMELESS is always at the top of my list. The creativity, the story, the writing, the people.  I was going to do a big 10 minute long story time, but thought it might get boring for y’all.. so instead, here’s a handful of pictures that maybe you haven’t seen before. Love to all my producers, writers and fellow actors and of course… TO THE CLOCKBLOCKERS!  Ps. I still hold out hope that one day the show will make a return. 😝

Back to work on Gabriel and Guardians in 2024! Head over to angel.com/gabriel to find out more and how YOU can actually OWN a piece of the show and be a co-creator.
